OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe workers getting 100%   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpay for 80% of the hours   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thousands of UK workers are starting a 
OL,6, four-day week trial from today.        
OL,8,FAround 70 companies are taking part in 
OL,9,Fwhat is thought to be the world's      
OL,10,Fbiggest pilot scheme into the working  
OL,11,Fpattern over the next six months.      
OL,13,FThe experiment has been organised by a 
OL,14,Fgroup campaigning for a shorter working
OL,15,Fweek, but for no loss in wages.        
OL,17,FDuring the trial, employees will get   
OL,18,F100% pay for 80% of the hours they     
OL,19,Fwould usually work, with the aim of    
OL,20,Fbeing more productive.                 
